seo_analysis.template:
Analyze the SEO performance of this {{resourceType}}:

Title: {{title}}
Description: {{description}}
Content: {{content}}

Shop Context:
- Name: {{shop.name}}
- Industry: {{shop.industry}}
- Target Audience: {{targetAudience}}

Brand Guidelines:
- Tone: {{brandGuidelines.tone}}
- Keywords: {{brandGuidelines.keywords}}
- Avoid Words: {{brandGuidelines.avoidWords}}

Please provide:
1. Overall SEO score (0-100)
2. Detailed analysis of:
   - Title optimization
   - Meta description effectiveness
   - Content quality and keyword usage
   - Image alt text (if applicable)
   - Technical SEO elements
3. Specific issues found with severity levels
4. Actionable recommendations prioritized by impact
5. Predicted traffic impact of implementing fixes

Format the response as structured JSON with clear metrics and explanations.

title_generation.template:
Generate 5 SEO-optimized titles for this {{resourceType}}:

Product/Content Details:
- Name: {{name}}
- Category: {{category}}
- Key Features: {{features}}
- Target Keywords: {{keywords}}

Shop Context:
- Shop Name: {{shop.name}}
- Industry: {{shop.industry}}
- Brand Voice: {{brandGuidelines.tone}}

Requirements:
- Length: 50-60 characters
- Include primary keywords naturally
- Match brand tone ({{brandGuidelines.tone}})
- Be compelling and click-worthy
- Avoid these words: {{brandGuidelines.avoidWords}}

For each title, provide:
1. The title text
2. Character count
3. Primary keywords used
4. Estimated CTR impact (1-10)
5. Brief explanation of strategy

Format as JSON array with these details for each title option.

