keyword_analysis.template:
Analyze keyword usage and opportunities for this {{resourceType}}:

Content Analysis:
- Title: {{title}}
- Description: {{description}}
- Content: {{content}}
- Current Keywords: {{currentKeywords}}

Keyword Research Context:
- Industry: {{shop.industry}}
- Target Audience: {{targetAudience}}
- Competitors: {{competitors}}
- Search Intent: {{searchIntent}}

Analysis Requirements:
1. Current keyword density analysis
2. Keyword distribution (title, headings, body, meta)
3. Missing keyword opportunities
4. LSI keyword suggestions
5. Long-tail keyword opportunities
6. Competitor keyword gaps
7. Search volume estimates (if known)
8. Keyword difficulty assessment

Provide recommendations for:
- Primary keywords (1-2)
- Secondary keywords (3-5)
- Long-tail keywords (5-10)
- LSI keywords (5-10)

Format as comprehensive JSON analysis with actionable insights.

